        x_coord - 2D x coordinate of node.
        y_coord - 2D x coordinate of node.
        x_coord_3d - 3D x coordinate of node.
        y_coord_3d - 3D y coordinate of node.
        short_name - The short abbreviated name of the node.
        long_name - The long official name of the node.
        floor - The floor the node is on.
